|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080203234420/http://www.fifa.com/worldfootball/clubfootball/news/newsid=536454.html
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。轉會費被估計大約在2000萬左右<ref>{{cite news 
|url=http://www.clarin.com/diario/2007/06/17/deportes/d-07401.htm 
|title=Los goles de Zárate valen 22 millones de dólares 
